reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome bookcase - sturdy and stylish!
reviews.reviewText: It’s been a long time since I’ve ordered this type of furniture online because I’m always afraid of the quality. Several years ago I made the mistake of ordering a dresser online and it fell apart within hours of assembling it. Well I saw this bookcase and I loved the color and style, so I took the plunge and ordered it. Boy oh boy, am I glad I did! It was easy to assemble (I put it together by myself in about 15 - 20 minutes). It’s relatively lightweight but it’s sturdy and it looks really nice. It’s not just some cheap plywood thrown together. It’s actually very well made and I expect it to last for years to come. The color is beautiful and honestly, the pictures don’t do it justice. It looks much nicer in person. I am using it in our bedroom as a tv stand and shelves and it’s the perfect height for our television. I love the little “cubby” style shelves. They are great for organizing things like Bluetooth speakers, keepsakes, candles and other decorative items that are commonly kept in the bedroom. It keeps our space looking organized and neat and it’s perfect for all kinds of things. I opted to leave the wheels off of ours because we have our TV on it and I don’t want it to roll. The cool part about that is also that It can be turned one of two ways depending on the height/length ratio needed (without the wheels attached, that is). However, if you’re using it for books or crafting supplies or maybe in your workshop, the wheels might come in very handy. It’s such a great bookcase and it’s versatile and functional. It adds style and organization and it’s great for any space. Very highly recommend!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best bookcase for smaller spaces
reviews.reviewText: Love this little bookcase as it provides more storage space than expected! I love how it has wheels too because it's so easy to move from room to room if needed. I like to switch up the look of rooms often and the wheels make doing so way easier. I also think it looks great in person and love the vintage wood finish. This bookcase works well in small spaces and makes organizing your small space a breeze. Assembly was fairly easy and took less time than most other pieces I've assembled lately. This one is definitely a keeper and recommend to literally everyone!
